 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Apr 02, 2015 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Lord,
</p>

 <p>
How would you have us known to the world?
</p>

 <p>
By whom we exclude? <br></br>
By what we hate? <br></br>
By whom we refuse to serve? <br></br>
By our purity?
</p>

 <p>
Instead, we are to be known <br></br>
by our loveâ€¦
</p>

 <p>
Love,
</p>

 <p>
in all its <br></br>
messy, <br></br>
entangled, <br></br>
accepting, <br></br>
and sometimes awkward <br></br>
beauty.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


